<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Thematic Research Areas</strong></h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">The particular area of focus is whether openness will provide added insights into the role of science, technology, and innovation (STI) in development practices, with the ultimate goal of strengthening local research capacity and informing policy.</p>
